data.description: Location location location! Come take a look at this charming 4 bedroom home in the heart of Yuma. Fresh exterior and interior paint, new fixtures throughout, remodeled hall and master bath, and plenty of space for a growing family! The 4th room has a fireplace and can be used as a bedroom, family room, or man cave! Schedule an appointment to see it before it's gone!
